Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:35.06,S3,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1534,853)}自行车的便利物件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:33.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话体温就不会流失了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:35.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
